69: ## Implementation Notes\n70: \n71: [TO BE FILLED: Implementation notes and patterns]\n72: \n73: ---\n74: \n75: ## References\n76: \n77: - cli-toolkit/design.md — CLI toolkit architecture\n78: - cli-toolkit/spec.md — CLI specification\n79: - AR-021 — CLI build command\n\n(End of file - total 79 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-022 — CLI publish 命令 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-022 — CLI publish 命令 |\n| Module | `cmd/cli` |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | L |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n[TO BE FILLED: Overview of the publish command functionality]\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n[TO BE FILLED: System context and component diagrams]\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-022/design.md","time":{"start":1775871067295,"end":1775871067303}}}}
